                        <p>I’m pretty sure you’ve got the time.</p>
<p><em>Dalia Dichter is a Trinity junior.</em></p>
<p><em>If you are having thoughts of suicide, call the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 800-273-TALK (8255) or text “START” to the Crisis Text Line at 741-741.</em></p>

